* Mobile application support
* Cloud-native deployment on IBM Cloud
* Deep Learning and Time-Series forecasting models for higher predictive accuracy

## Final Remark

**Rising Waters** demonstrates the practical application of Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning in solving a critical environmental challenge. By combining data analysis, predictive modeling, and a web-based deployment platform, the project provides an intelligent and scalable flood prediction solution. It serves as a strong example of how data-driven technologies can contribute to disaster risk reduction, improve public safety, and support sustainable environmental management in an increasingly climate-sensitive world.

